Mon Jul 20 08:42:49 UTC 2026 - Dirk Müller <dmueller@suse.com>

- update to 5.0.12:
  * Added "My Folders" to left navigation.
  * Fix checked-resource count and picked-resource merge bugs
  * Remember picked selections even after they are de-selected
  * For javascript coverage, also generate cobertura style
    reports
  * In tox, build the girder web client
  * Fix a test fixture to work with uvicorn 0.50
  * Check if /dev/fuse exists before running tests requiring it
  * add `-e` flag to `pip install` for web tests
  * Update packages in the package locks
  * **Full Changelog**:
    https://github.com/girder/girder/compare/v5.0.11...v5.0.12
- update to 5.0.11:
  * Upgrade to node 22 for testing
  * Adjust where tox builds docs
  * Correct registration policy values in docs
  * Fix an RST format issue
  * #2416 Rename "Quick Search" to "Search"
  * Check that a local worker is running
  * Propagate policy errors in OAuth2 flow
  * Hide search popovers when clicking away
  * Allow to overwrite emails sent due to various auth policies
  * Update the vite config
- update to 5.0.10:
  * Add sphinx-llm
  * Adjust redis socket_timeout
  * **Full Changelog**:
    https://github.com/girder/girder/compare/v5.0.9...v5.0.10
- update to 5.0.9:
  * Reduce spurious warning about index creation
  * Fix unbuffered asgi downloads.
  * **Full Changelog**:
    https://github.com/girder/girder/compare/v5.0.8...v5.0.9
- update to 5.0.8:
  * Update environment docs
  * Ensure we are not using stale or duplicate headers
  * **Full Changelog**:
    https://github.com/girder/girder/compare/v5.0.7...v5.0.8
- update to 5.0.7:
  * When uploading, add a default mime type
  * docs: update migration guide for async events
  * Add the ability to reserve space on filesystem assetstores
  * **Full Changelog**:
    https://github.com/girder/girder/compare/v5.0.6...v5.0.7

